# 🛍️ SNITCH E-Commerce – Product Variants System

## 🚀 Overview

This feature introduces a **dynamic product variant system** for the SNITCH E-Commerce platform. It allows sellers to create multiple variants of a product and enables buyers to interactively select variants on the product detail page.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🧑‍💼 Seller Side

* Create product variants
* Manage stock per variant
* Add variant-specific images
* Define attributes (color, size, etc.)
* Set custom pricing for variants

### 🧑‍💻 Buyer Side

* Select product variants dynamically
* View updated images, price, and stock
* Smooth UI interaction (real-time updates)
* Automatic fallback to default product values

---

## 🧠 Core Concept

Each product can have **multiple variants**, and each variant can override:

* Images
* Price
* Stock
* Attributes

If a variant does NOT contain a field →
👉 fallback to main product value

---

## 🔁 Fallback Logic

```js
const displayImages = variant.images?.length
  ? variant.images
  : product.images;

const displayPrice = variant.price || product.price;
```

